<SSRControls>
<!-- 
Nov 2011 Tom R
* Reinstituted the ShellholesToPalm and CragsToPalm rules, replacing ShellholesToPalmTrees and CragsToPalmTrees, which unfortunately invoked the (Orch2)PalmTrees rule

Apr 2011 Tom R
* Added Dense Jungle, Bamboo, SwampPattern, Light Woods, DTO Broken Terrain, and DTO Steppe Terrain checkboxes to Other Transformations
* Added Orchards To Cactus Patches, ShellholesToCactusPatches, CragsToCactusPatches, and Orch2Palm rules in OSC Swapping
* Added DTO terrain to Terrain dropdown, made "use desert colors" and "use ETO colors"
    activate on DTO and ETO terrain, respectively 
* Added FloodedStreams, FloodedRivers and FordableRivers rules
* Added StreamsToGullies rule
* Enabled everything in the PTO to be turned off except SwampToSwampPattern (ie, all of the PTO rules are activated by the sourceproperty of PTO light or dense jungle (and can thus be deactivated), not dictated automatically by PTO light or dense jungle
* Removed the <source/> for Mud and NoBridge; also removed the NoBridge activating under NoRoads
* Cleaned up the </entry> fields - must have one for every entry that is activated by a sourceproperty (ie, that is a Target)
* Put DTO and PTO stuff into their own panels

Aug 2008 Tom R
* added Rice Paddies to the Transformation rules
* removed the L2,3,4 To Vineyard transformation rules

Jan 2008  Tom R
* v5 board changes (added "Board X Special Overlays" menu)
* revamped the Walls/Hedges menu

Aug 20, 2002 Tom R
* Removed the auto DTOtoETO rule under the ETO Terrain option
* Moved the DTO Terrain menu option down to a checkbox under "Other Transformations" as "DTO Colors", along with an "ETO Colors" checkbox
* Added "orchards out of season" text when that rule is invoked
* Fixed text on wall/hedge to cactus hedge

Aug 19, 2002 Tom R
* Added DTOtoETO and ETOtoDTO rules, with DTO entry under the Terrain menu

Aug 16, 2002 Tom R
* Added Rice Paddy menu item to Water Level menu
* Removed Orch2Vineyard from OSC Swapping menu

July 7, 2002 Tom R
* Added Crag2Palm choice
* Added "Other Xformations" menu for X2(Vineyard)
* Moved Wall/Hedge to CactusHedge to the Wall/Hedge menu
* Added Orch2(CactusPatch/OliveGrove/Vineyard) options under OSC menu
* Added Crag2Vineyard option under OSC menu

July 3, 2002 Tom R
Changes:
* Added NoCliffs checkbox which is auto-activated under NoHills
* Added NoGrain rule to Snow and Deep Snow
* Snow and Deep Snow auto-check OrchardOutOfSeason (added <source/>
  line to Snow menu to allow this)
* Added <Source/> line after Roads menu name entry to allow NoBridges to
  activate under NoRoads
* Added OSC Swapping menu 
-->
   <Basic>
